n一來有人信咗佢講既嘢，雖然呢啲人都係垃圾黎，完全唔識用大腦思考，垃圾世柒講一句佢就信一句<br />\n二來啲view數養住呢條仆街係度大放厥詞，食人血饅頭<br />\n所以狙擊呢條仆街冇用，條友係德國，你做乜都好都吹佢唔漲，佢仲可以屈9你逼害佢<br />\n要搞就搞9佢啲支持者 聽眾，現實生活中見親有人聽黃世柒一定要狠狠地笑同屌9佢地<br />\n到有朝一日呢條友冇咩人聽，冇晒影響力，話撚得知佢又屈邊個係鬼"},{"pid":"5a878662e116e1b32b889720431937645fa0e540","tid":2498952,"uid":130079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:19:59.000Z","msg":"黃世澤評論太戇鳩"},{"pid":"294674c6662960cbf82cc2f80f2d2299064d8649","tid":2498952,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98f4b02b27157da0c078675e5a9183aa23e014b7","tid":2498952,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14669d43a067529adf9e5a9cf6b2512e9d6d45d2","tid":2498952,"uid":81190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"認真，劉細良賣樓黃世澤有冇幫手做agent？<br />\n<br />\n啲錢黃世澤有冇得分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"佢當國父說項拍咗段22分鐘，又賺多筆廣告錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"點解賺埋賺埋咁多都唔去洗下牙<br />\n<br />\n洗下牙姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e86b4d5f6281a4a9495bfccbe1fb7b13057bed","tid":2498952,"uid":14718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a878662e116e1b32b889720431937645fa0e540","tid":2498952,"uid":130079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:19:59.000Z","msg":"黃世澤評論太戇鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"戇鳩得過信佢講嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6054f44e9121de31c4686810878e2407e8c20fd8","tid":2498952,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31e86b4d5f6281a4a9495bfccbe1fb7b13057bed","tid":2498952,"uid":14718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a878662e116e1b32b889720431937645fa0e540","tid":2498952,"uid":130079,"like":3,"disl